      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented verification test suite with version-controlled release notes and traceable build process.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 used with documented QA procedures including regression test suite. Software version control and release documentation confirm compliance with MRL 2 requirements."
    },
