      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted with 2.1M, 6.4M, and 14.7M element meshes. Richardson extrapolation yields GCI of 2.3% for the relative hemolysis index, exceeding MRL 2 requirement. Fine mesh selected for production runs."
