    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 guidance for Class II devices at medium model influence. Relative hemolysis index satisfies RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating points. Mesh convergence GCI of 2.3% is within acceptable bounds. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device.",
